name: MATH 1
description: Created by @MathMakesArt (https://mathmakesart) on 2021-04-16. This image contains the generative frame which I typically use as my profile image, cut to a circular profile and surrounded by a ring of inner diameter 1000 pixels and outer diameter 1080 pixels. This mint is intended for experimental purposes and the image is meant to serve more as a visual placeholder and less as art. Royalties are set to 10 percent, the default platform value.
